FBIS4-38033 "drnes124_j_94026" FBIS-NES-94-124 Daily Report 27 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Fierce Battles Continue to Rage Near Aden Fierce Battles Continue to Rage Near Aden South Claims Plane Downed, Tanks Destroyed NC2706211094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2030 GMT 27 Jun 94 NC2706211094 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Text] Cairo, 27 Jun (MENA) -- A military source in Aden today said that southern forces downed one of several northern planes that were trying to bombard Aden's oil refineries. In a statement faxed to MENA tonight, the source said that southern troops destroyed six tanks and killed, wounded, or captured hundreds of northern troops.
